[SPEAKER_01] pa su stisli bankare,

641
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] a naravno bankari neće su zli.

642
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:11,519
[SPEAKER_01] U tom trenutku je moja percepcija bila drugačija.

643
00:42:11,519 --> 00:42:13,960
